posting_body: ['Welcome home to Powers Ridge Senior Living!', 'Located at:', '1351 Lake Dr W', 'Chanhassen, MN 55317', 'Rental Information:', '# of Bedrooms: 2', '# of Bathrooms:  2', 'Square Footage: 1066 sq ft', 'Rental Pricing: $2074/month', 'Contact our leasing office at', 'show contact info', 'Offering One-, Two-, and Three-Bedroom Apartments.', "Imagine all the comforts of home with the luxuries you've always desired, but never wanted to maintain!", "Exceptional 55+ Independendent Living is what you'll find at Powers Ridge Senior Living.", 'Spacious, well appointed apartments with luxury finishes, secured entry, and access to Powers Ridge Club House make Powers Ridge the perfect choice for premier retirement living!', 'Powers Ridge is designed with the idea that you make the rules.', 'You can unwind by the indoor pool and spa at the Powers Ridge Club House or simply relax on your own.', 'Choices are what we are all about at Powers Ridge Senior Living!', 'Powers Ridge is proudly managed by Peak Living.', 'At Peak Living, our mission is to provide the highest quality property management services in the industry.', 'We achieve this through our greatest asset; our people.', 'Our on-site and regional management teams offer unsurpassed customer service and local expertise for those living at our properties and for our clients.', 'Our experiences and entrepreneurial spirit mean that we understand that no two buildings or clients are the same, and as such, flexibility and adaptability are key to achieving investment goals.', 'Through the use of the latest technologies, Peak Living is able to provide exceptional accounting/reporting as well as industry leading portal functionality for prospective and current residents, including digital lease signing, online work order submission, and online payments.', 'Community Features:', '❖ Business Center', '❖ Car Wash Area', '❖ Clubhouse', '❖ Elevator', '❖ Grill', '❖ Indoor Pool', '❖ Onsite Salon', '❖ Recycling', '❖ Smoke-Free', '❖ Spa', '❖ Community-Wide WiFi', '❖ Controlled Access', '❖ Disposal Chutes', '❖ Fitness Center', '❖ Guest Apartment', '❖ Large Community Deck with Gas Grill', '❖ On Call Maintenance Available', '❖ On-Site Management', '❖ Professionally Designed and Maintained Landscape', '❖ Resident Services Portal with Online Payment & Maintenance Request Options', 'Unit Features:', '❖ Central Heating & Air Conditioning', '❖ Dishwasher', '❖ Extra Storage', '❖ Free Cable', '❖ Granite Countertops', '❖ Heated Underground Parking', '❖ Microwave', '❖ Patio/Balcony', '❖ Range', '❖ Refrigerator', 'Office Hours:', 'Mon - Fri: 8:00 AM - 4:00 PM', 'show contact info', 'Pet Policy:', 'Dogs and Cats Allowed: $25 Monthly Pet Rent.', 'Nonrefundable $500 Fee. 60 lb Weight Limit.', '2 Pet Limit.', 'Leasing Options:', '6-Month, 12-Month', 'Website:', '<URL>/', 'Management:', 'Peak Living', 'EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY', '9E6D0B5E94484552']
